Rust has the Best Names

Posted on August 19, 2018 by Noah Ryan

I’ve been looking into Rust recently, and I am finding that I like it, and that I want to like it.

If nothing else, that language community choses the best names for things:

  • Rust
  • Deisal
  • Refraction
  • Iron
  • Nickel
  • Servo
  • Tendril

and probably many more. I just can’t help but like them.
